popularityCurve.label: lotus cars usa inc is pleased to announce the 35th anniversary commemorative edition type 72d this exclusive collectible edition model memorializes one of the finest formula 1 designs of all time the lotus 72 it was in this vehicle that the legendary emerson fittipaldi proved unstoppable winning five of eleven races in 1972 thus becoming the youngest champion in f1 history
